channel.title: First sig in a while lol
channel.description:
well here is my first sig in a while... no brushes used because i didnt have any at the time... anyways took like 20 min to make so it sucks in my opinion... also its a girl because it was the very first render on planetrenders and i didnt feel like looking for another render lol and yes the font sucks and does not go with the thing at all.. its the only font i thought looked good i need to find some :P
[IMG]http://i87.photobucket.com/albums/k135/dh713/girlsig.jpg[/img]
